Both required output files written. Schema-validated transcript.json (25 iterations) and analysis_summary.txt are in `C:\Users\klkehl\are_llms_biased\data\ds001\tasks\breast\anonymized\`.

**Headline finding:** `feature_013` is a randomly assigned treatment (~35% prevalence, balanced across covariates). It increases `pfs_months` by ~4.65 months in the favorable subgroup (`feature_029=1` AND `feature_028=0` AND `feature_018=0` AND `feature_033 ≤ ~15`; n=11,575) and has no clinically meaningful effect (~+0.2 months) elsewhere. Within the `feature_029=0` stratum, the treatment is null in every combination of the other modifiers — `feature_029=1` is necessary. `feature_033` further attenuates the treatment effect at -0.135 months/unit even within the otherwise favorable strata.

The full prognostic + treatment-interaction model reaches R² = 0.976. Pure prognostic factors that do NOT modify the treatment effect: `feature_005`, `feature_006`, `feature_001`, `feature_012`, `feature_004`, `feature_024`, `feature_031`. Apparent modifiers `feature_023` and `feature_016` are shadows of `feature_029` (r=+0.67) and `feature_018` (r=-0.36).
